Falana has become a victim of kidnappers in Zaria, Kaduna State. National Daily learned that an Officer of the Nigerian Army, Lieutenant Falana has been kidnapped in Zaria, opposite Ahmadu Bello University (ABU), Zaria, this Tuesday afternoon.
It was gathered that the Kidnappers zoomed off with their victim’s white Toyota Corolla Car (Tinted).
Signal has been sent to officers on duty along Zaria – Kano, Zara -Jos, Zaria – Birnin- Gwari and Zaria Kaduna road to watch out for the Car.
Kidnapping has of security operatives have been worrisome to the Nigerian government over time.
Details later.







			
